---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Tile & Backsplash — Ardmore, Main Line & Philadelphia
description: A full Daltile showroom in Ardmore plus natural stone and glass mosaics — set across the Main Line and Greater Philadelphia by the same crew that installs your counters.
permalink: /tile/
---

<div class="page-head page-head--split">
  <div>
    <span class="kicker">Tile &amp; Backsplash</span>
    <h1>The finishing layer.</h1>
  </div>
  <p class="lede lede--sm" style="max-width:40ch">A full Daltile showroom plus natural stone and glass mosaics — set by the same crew that installs your counters.</p>
</div>

<div class="grid grid--3" style="padding:8px var(--pad-x) 56px; gap:28px 20px">
  {% for c in tile %}
    <div class="card">
      {% if c.image %}
        <div class="photo"><img src="{{ c.image }}" alt="{{ c.alt }}" loading="lazy"></div>
      {% else %}
        {% set c1 = c.bg.split(',') | first %}
        {% set c2 = c.bg.split(',') | last %}
        <div class="ph" style="background:repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, {{ c1 }}, {{ c1 }} 10px, {{ c2 }} 10px, {{ c2 }} 20px)">
          <span>{{ c.name | lower }} sample</span>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
      <span class="card__title card__title--lg">{{ c.name }}</span>
      <span class="card__meta" style="font-size:13px">{{ c.desc }}</span>
    </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<p style="margin:0;padding:0 var(--pad-x) 40px;font:400 12px var(--sans);color:var(--faint)">Room scenes courtesy of Daltile. WGMT is an authorized Daltile dealer.</p>

<div class="section" style="padding-top:0">
  <div class="section-head">
    <h2>Browse the Daltile catalog</h2>
    <p class="lede lede--sm" style="max-width:44ch">Flip through the full product catalog right here, or take it with you — Daltile&rsquo;s ProExchange app puts products, pricing, and ordering on your phone.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="embed-note" style="margin:0 0 24px">
    <span class="kicker" style="font-size:11px">Product catalog · PDF</span>
    <p>Viewing on a phone? <a href="https://digitalassets.daltile.com/content/dam/Daltile/website/resources/products/product-catalogs/DAL_2017_Catalog_Final_WebHQ.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open the catalog in a new tab</a> — it&rsquo;s easier to pinch and zoom.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="embed-frame" style="margin:0 0 32px">
    <iframe src="https://digitalassets.daltile.com/content/dam/Daltile/website/resources/products/product-catalogs/DAL_2017_Catalog_Final_WebHQ.pdf" title="Daltile product catalog (PDF)" loading="lazy"></iframe>
  </div>

  <div class="app-links">
    <span class="app-links__label">Get the Daltile ProExchange app:</span>
    <a class="btn btn--outline" href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/proexchange-by-dal-tile/id1554347467" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#63743; App Store — iPhone &amp; iPad</a>
    <a class="btn btn--outline" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.daltile.proexchange" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ Google Play — Android</a>
  </div>
</div>

{% set cta = { text: "Bringing a backsplash idea? We’ll match it to your stone.", button: "Plan a Showroom Visit" } %}
